      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy paint oxidation, several large dents, and visible rust along the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention, and the transmission shifts roughly. The interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and a persistent musty odor. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical skills or a source for spare parts.",
